&gt; &gt; an officially registered relation type here:
&gt; &gt;
&gt; &gt; * http://www.iana.org/assignments/link-relations/link-relations.xml
&gt; &gt;
&gt; &gt; * http://www.w3.org/TR/html401/types.html#h-6.12
&gt; &gt;
